    com.liferay.portal.kernel.struts.StrutsAction

    public class RedirectAction
extends com.liferay.portal.kernel.struts.BaseStrutsAction
    RedirectAction class extends BaseStrutsAction class and override its execute method. This method is used for redirecting to studios edit page automatically after the user who has a role 'Studio Owner' integrate Instagram with their studio account.
